text: Nothing much going on here. The businesses were probably affected by the construction around them.

Came to this area to attend a childbirth course at Thomson Medical. Nothing to eat here just 1 coffeeshop with little to nothing to eat after 6pm. Your best bet is the gas station nearby. There are more vacant shops than occupied, not much of a “shopping centre”.
This shopping centre doesn't appear popular as there are more vacant shop houses than the one that are occupied.
They have several nice shops. This mall is a great place to visit.
Shopping center nice place for shopping or hang out. Many shops n kopitiams and etc.
